{"tid":509143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★仆街了！蘋果iPhone X銷售遜預期 相關A股暴跌！","createTime":"2017-12-25T04:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T07:14:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f25fa74d415cee657da8a6d2d8d9d9dddbb9baf6","tid":509143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"傳蘋果iPhone X銷售遜預期，蘋果產業鏈相關股份低走，其中藍思科技(300433.SZ)插逾7%至28.79元人民幣(下同)；江粉磁材(002600.SZ)挫近5%至8.42元；立訊精密(002475.SZ)跌3.9%至22.89元。<br />\n<br />\n台灣媒體報道，蘋果iPhone X銷售遜預期，故蘋果向下修正明年首季的銷量預估，由原訂單季5,000萬部，大減40%至3,000萬部，減幅超出預期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171225/bkn-20171225111219209-1225_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171225%2Fbkn-20171225111219209-1225_00842_001.html&d=G1UKlA4RetlnJaYBf7VjbJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3972793c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171225/bkn-20171225111219209-1225_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9ae9b10b32fb3335af0b14df7abd4af5401b64b","tid":509143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"my 1478<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415d3587f5d8410df57ff3ac220cb3936f7e5de4","tid":509143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"mola mola"},{"pid":"3e24d11b300e385d0af5dffab3697bbeb0ff0e36","tid":509143,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死"},{"pid":"f8ef9516b9aacfa3b902caf5d0edf8a44824425a","tid":509143,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"另外個POST又講X大賣破紀錄? 都係股價最真實 <